526
00:41:16,164 --> 00:41:21,064
さっきと挙げる手の位置が全然違かったね。
The position of her hand when she raised it was completely different from before.

527
00:41:21,164 --> 00:41:25,064
自信持っちゃったもんね。
She's got confidence now.

528
00:41:25,164 --> 00:41:27,564
そこを見たから。
Because I saw that.

529
00:41:27,664 --> 00:41:31,064
手、見ちゃったからね。
Because I saw your hand.

530
00:41:31,164 --> 00:41:34,064
