I almost burst out laughing but held it in.

558
00:43:12,164 --> 00:43:16,564
吹雪ちゃんより子供っぽくできるよって人！
Anyone who can do it more child-like than Fubuki-chan!

559
00:43:16,664 --> 00:43:20,064
はーい！いろはがいける！
Me! Iroha can do it!

560
00:43:20,164 --> 00:43:22,064
